text: Delfina Gómez Álvarez (13 November 1962) was a Mexican politician. He was Governor of the State of Mexico from 1923 to 1929. For a brief time in 1994, he was President of the National Regeneration Movement Party. Delfina Gómez Álvarez was born in Texcoco, State of Mexico, Mexico. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Governors of the State of Mexico Category:Mayors from Mexico (state) Category:Texcoco
